  %% Diagram 67: Influencer Affiliate and Referral Attribution Lifecycle

  Issue[Issue affiliate/referral link or code]
  Click[Track click event]
  Visit[Buyer session attribution]
  CodeCheck{Code valid and unexpired?}
  Convert{Order conversion happened?}

  Validate[Validate attribution window + anti-fraud checks]
  Valid{Attribution valid?}

  Reward[Post affiliate commission/reward]
  PayoutSignal[Emit commission payout signal]
  Ledger[(Update affiliate_tracking/referral_codes)]
  Report[Expose payout and performance report]

  NoCredit[No attribution credit]
  Review[Hold for fraud or anomaly review]

  Issue --> Click --> Visit --> CodeCheck
  CodeCheck -- No --> NoCredit
  CodeCheck -- Yes --> Convert
  Convert -- No --> NoCredit
  Convert -- Yes --> Validate --> Valid

  Valid -- Yes --> Reward --> PayoutSignal --> Ledger --> Report
  Valid -- No --> NoCredit
  Validate -->|Fraud-like anomaly| Review --> NoCredit
